                                    <td align="center" style="box-sizing:border-box;min-width: 590px;">
                                        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="590" style="box-sizing:border-box;min-width: 590px; background-color: white; padding: 0px 8px 0px 8px; border-collapse:collapse;">
                                            <tbody style="box-sizing:border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing:border-box;"><td valign="top" style="box-sizing:border-box;font-size: 13px;">
                                                <div style="font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;font-size:13px;">
                                                    Dear --name--
                                                    <br>
                                                    <br style="box-sizing:border-box;">Welcome onboard to HiiBoss and congratulations on your new subscription. You can get started with it right away and we hope you will enjoy our services.

Please activate your active subscription by clicking the button below:<br style="box-sizing:border-box;"><br style="box-sizing:border-box;">
                                                        <a href="--url_object--" style="border-style:solid;cursor:pointer;text-transform:uppercase;transition-property:none;transition-delay:0s;transition-timing-function:ease;transition-duration:0s;line-height:1.5;border-left-color:#7F56D9;border-bottom-color:#7F56D9;border-right-color:#7F56D9;border-top-color:#7F56D9;border-left-width:1px;border-bottom-width:1px;border-right-width:1px;border-top-width:1px;user-select:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;font-weight:500;display:inline-block;background-color:#7F56D9;color:#ffffff;box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 16px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 13px;" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary flat btn-lg">Click to activate your instance</a>
<br style="box-sizing:border-box;"><div style="font-family:&quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;font-size:13px;margin: 16px 0px 16px 0px;">

If you have questions about this activation, your subscription, or would just like to chat, contact us at any time. We'd love to hear from you. View our <a style="color:#7F56D9" href="/contactus">Online Support </a>  for more information too.</div>
                                                   <br style="box-sizing:border-box;"> <t t-set="website_url" t-value="object.get_base_url()" data-oe-t-inline="true" style="box-sizing:border-box;"></t>You can also sign in to the <a style="color:#7F56D9" href="/my/home">Customer Portal </a> to manage your account and view your transactions and payments.
<br style="box-sizing:border-box;"><br style="box-sizing:border-box;">
                                                    Thank you,<br style="box-sizing:border-box;">
                                                    <br style="box-sizing:border-box;">HiiBoss Pte Ltd

                                            </div></td></tr>
                                            <tr style="box-sizing:border-box;"><td style="box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;">
                                              <hr width="100%" style="border-style:none;border-top-width:medium;border-left-width:medium;border-bottom-width:medium;border-right-width:medium;overflow-y:visible;overflow-x:visible;height:0px;box-sizing:content-box;background-color:#cccccc;border:medium none;clear:both;display:block;font-size:0px;min-height:1px;line-height:0; margin: 16px 0px 16px 0px;" contenteditable="false">
                                            </td></tr>
                                        </tbody></table>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <!-- FOOTER -->
                                <tr>
                                    <td valign="middle" align="left" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 11px;">--company_name--</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td valign="middle" align="left" style="opacity: 0.7; font-size: 11px;">--company_street--
                                                <br/>
                                                --company_phone-- | <a href="mailto:--company_email--" style="box-sizing:border-box;background-color:transparent;text-decoration:none; color: #454748;" contenteditable="false">--company_email--</a> | <a href="--company_website--" style="box-sizing:border-box;background-color:transparent;text-decoration:none; color: #454748;"  contenteditable="false">--company_website--</a><br/><br/>
